{"tid":543688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【置業陷阱】盲搶樓誤購凶宅 金獅花園撻定料蝕20萬","createTime":"2018-01-28T17:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T00:30:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"41e26dba09b0228edc430fb851ba470d2de652ff","tid":543688,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180128/large/1517136270_e2f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180128%2Flarge%2F1517136270_e2f1.jpg&h=7de4b948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓市瘋狂，市民盲搶樓變誤購凶宅，損失慘重。消息指，大圍金獅花園金安閣一個低層單位，實用面積321方呎，早數天以433萬元售出，呎價13,489元，較個別銀行估值高出6%。此單位分別獲中銀及滙豐網上估值408萬及454萬元。有區內代理表示，買家最終撻定離場。撻定原因，據聞是買家在購入單位後方知道自己所買入的是一個凶宅戶，價錢亦貼近市價，與正常單位沒有分別。<br />\n按二手樓正常買賣，買家於簽定臨時買賣合約時一般先支付樓價3%定金﹔若以此作參考及須向地產代理賠償的雙倍佣金，買家今次誤購凶宅而撻定，有可能損失逾20萬元。<br />\n本報翻查土地註冊處資料，上址一名前任80歲業主，2001年於屋內吊頸自殺身亡﹔死者的死亡證明書已交付土地註冊處註冊登記。<br />\n買家撻定後，業主現將單位減價重新放盤，叫價425萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180128/57764593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57764593&d=9YKHrMJwdctXi9TL31ylgGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=5b418d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57764593&h=f20c3b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180128/57764593</a>"},{"pid":"bbce5fc77be7f6a5403b4c3d1058467642c301b8","tid":543688,"uid":56401,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T18:08:46.000Z","msg":"平幾皮既凶宅 得狗同香港人同呀差想接"},{"pid":"478b96ea134f59dfed2294127a1b76cfd1b44f5e","tid":543688,"uid":41508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"919d5e3f0a081e8412ffe7628d11bf47a3bc5d6e","tid":5